{"tid":2354891,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Trump簽署行政命令 ban 支付寶 WeChatPay","createTime":"2021-01-05T23:14:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T01:13:17.000Z","uid":41404,"like":53,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1b5a69a36a02737ddef2b93ee268b75c96e0e17d","tid":2354891,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T23:14:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/BigStory12/idUSKBN29A2PA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2FBigStory12%2FidUSKBN29A2PA&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAGyNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=b4148aa4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2FBigStory12%2FidUSKBN29A2PA&h=270658c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/BigStory12/idUSKBN29A2PA</a>"},{"pid":"7e0d2b9bf9a1281e814c320b91932e6880131370","tid":2354891,"uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T23:15:15.000Z","msg":"WASHINGTON (Reuters) - U.S. President Donald Trump on Tuesday signed an executive order banning transactions with eight Chinese software applications, including Ant Group&rsquo;s Alipay, a senior administration official said, escalating tensions with Beijing before President-elect Joe Biden takes office this month.<br />\n<br />\nThe order, first reported by Reuters, tasks the Commerce Department with defining which transactions will be banned under the directive and targets Tencent Holdings Ltd&rsquo;s QQ Wallet and WeChat pay as well.<br />\n<br />\nThe move is aimed at curbing the threat to Americans posed by Chinese software applications, which have large user bases and access to sensitive data, the official said."},{"pid":"283233271128be50e486e337cf81acdb4dcd27a0","tid":2354891,"uid":28279,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T23:16:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />過多陣就解返"},{"pid":"1579bb1a54abda